<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>



If you encounter issues with the Git pull functionality, check the following:



<ol><li>**User Permissions**: Ensure the user has the 'admin' role in their session</li></ol>

<ol><li>**URL Routing**: Verify that the URL is correctly set to <code>/admin/git_pull</code></li></ol>

<ol><li>**Application Logs**: Check the application logs for detailed error messages</li></ol>

<ol><li>**Debug Mode**: Enable debug mode to see additional information on the page</li></ol>

<ol><li>**Git Repository**: Ensure the Git repository is properly configured</li></ol>



